: tranglorencontact@gmail.com;\r\n\r\n- Gửi tin nhắn tới số: 093.609.5589 (cô Trang) hoặc 0913.281.608 (thầy Thắng)\r\nHoặc\r\nwww.trangloren.com\r\n\r\nTrangloren','publish','open','closed','','effective-academic-writing','','','2017-05-11 07:31:40','2017-05-11 07:31:40','',0,'http://trangloren.com/?post_type=schedule&#038;p=1920',0,'schedule','',0),(1921,1,'2017-05-10 08:22:16','2017-05-10 08:22:16','','256646_c49f_7','','inherit','open','closed','','256646_c49f_7','','','2017-05-10 08:22:16','2017-05-10 08:22:16','',1920,'http://trangloren.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/256646_c49f_7.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(1922,1,'2017-05-10 08:22:38','2017-05-10 08:22:38','','Effective Academic Writing','','inherit','closed','closed','','1920-revision-v1','','','2017-05-10 08:22:38','2017-05-10 08:22:38','',1920,'http://trangloren.com/1920-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(1923,1,'2017-05-08 10:38:24','2017-05-08 10:38:24','Bộ sách bom tấn\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1924\" src=\"http://trangloren.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18275122_1900403640240009_24201388904633955_n.jpg\" alt=\"18275122_1900403640240009_24201388904633955_n\" width=\"602\" height=\"403\" /></p>\r\nLần đầu tiên nhà xuất bản nổi tiếng Oxford ra mắt chuỗi tài liệu mang tinh chuyên ngành cho hơn 30 lĩnh vực phổ biến từ tài chính, ngân hàng tới công nghệ, dầu mỏ.\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1938\" src=\"http://trangloren.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18342451_1900403776906662_4522571315914274268_n.jpg\" alt=\"18342451_1900403776906662_4522571315914274268_n\" width=\"960\" height=\"452\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1937\" src=\"http://trangloren.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/18301917_1900403810239992_6956716518540052519_n.jpg\" alt=\"18301917_1900403810239992_6956716518540052519_n\" width=\"960\" height=\"452\" /></p>\r\nSách được thiết kế đẹp mắt với các chủ đề mang tính thời sự h